+| [networkSecurityPerimeterConfigurationsListByServiceSample.js][networksecurityperimeterconfigurationslistbyservicesample] | gets a list of network security perimeter configurations for a search service. x-ms-original-file: 2026-03-01-preview/NetworkSecurityPerimeterConfigurationsListByService.json                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
