+| [privateEndpointConnectionsUpdateSample.js][privateendpointconnectionsupdatesample]                                       | updates a private endpoint connection to the search service in the given resource group. x-ms-original-file: 2026-03-01-preview/UpdatePrivateEndpointConnection.json                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
+| [privateLinkResourcesListSupportedSample.js][privatelinkresourceslistsupportedsample]                                     | gets a list of all supported private link resource types for the given service. x-ms-original-file: 2026-03-01-preview/ListSupportedPrivateLinkResources.json                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
+| [queryKeysCreateSample.js][querykeyscreatesample]                                                                         | generates a new query key for the specified search service. You can create up to 50 query keys per service. x-ms-original-file: 2026-03-01-preview/SearchCreateQueryKey.json                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
